<lb n="0904b02"/><head type="no">No. 1383</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0904b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0904006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說宿命智陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0904b04"/>
<lb n="0904b05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0904007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西天…師））十八字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0904007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師）十八字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0904007"><lem>西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0904b06"/>明教大師</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿明教大師</rdg></app><note n="0904008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臣〕－【三】</note><note n="0904008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔臣〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0904008"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0904b07"/><p>爾時世尊告阿難言。有陀羅尼名宿命智。若
<lb n="0904b08"/>有眾生聞是陀羅尼。能<note n="0904009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝至【元】【明】</note><app n="0904009"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>心受持者。所有千
<lb n="0904b09"/>劫之中極重罪業皆悉消<note n="0904010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅＝除【明】</note><app n="0904010"><lem>滅</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">除</rdg></app>。若能終身不間
<lb n="0904b10"/>斷者。是人於七俱胝生常知宿命。即說陀羅
<lb n="0904b11"/>尼曰</p>
<lb n="0904b12"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0904011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵字載於卷末</note>那謨<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0904012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【元】【明】</note><app n="0904012"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>室詰泥<note place="inline">去聲呼下同一</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;
<lb n="0904b13"/>多<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>阿囉曷<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>三藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱
<lb n="0904b14"/><note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline"><app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K34_p0479b15" cf2="Q33_p0208a17">三</lem><rdg wit="【大】">二</rdg></app></note>怛&CB00853;他<note place="inline">引四</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合</note>囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合五</note>
<lb n="0904b15"/>蘇囉怛泥<note place="inline">二合六</note>囉怛努<note place="inline">二合引</note>訥婆<note place="inline">二合</note>味<note place="inline">引七</note>摩
<lb n="0904b16"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>枳囉尼<note place="inline">去聲八</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>三婆
<lb n="0904b17"/>味<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引九</note></p>
<lb n="0904b18"/><p>爾時阿難聞佛宣說。令諸眾生得宿命智陀
<lb n="0904b19"/>羅尼已。歎未曾有歡喜無量。即以頭頂禮佛
<lb n="0904b20"/>而退</p>
<lb n="0904b21"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說宿命智陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
